last_play.text: Andrew McCutchen grounds out to shortstop, Nick Madrigal to Frank Schwindel.
Myles Straw called out on strikes.
Kevin Newman grounds out to shallow infield to Ryan Helsley.
Alcides Escobar flies out to shallow center field to Jeff McNeil.
Tyler Wade grounds out to second base. Mike Trout out at second.
Seth Beer homers to right field. Carson Kelly scores. Jake McCarthy scores.
